[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "お母様。連れてまいりました",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "……ただいま、母さん",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ハイディ！　あなた、いったい今までどこに居たの！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "ごほん！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "その格好もなんなの？\nまともな暮らしができていたとは思えない――",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "ごほん、ごほん！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……ごめんなさい。\nこんなことを言いたかったわけじゃないはずなのに",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "……手紙、読んだよ。\nとにかく助けに来たから、ちゃんと事情を話して",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "ここからは、どうぞお二人で。\n私はこのまま外で警戒しております",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "それじゃあ、中に入りましょう。\n着替えも用意しておくわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "着替え？　いいよこのままの格好で！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "いいって言ったのに",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あなたのために用意してたんだから\n着ていってちょうだい",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "色々言いたいことも、言わなきゃいけないことも\nあるけれど……ひとまず、今の話をしましょう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "うん。そうだね。まずは、今回の件を解決しよう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……きっかけは、あの人の不正に気付いたことだった。\nあの人は、やってはいけないことをしたのよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "……もしかして、ねつ造とか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ええ。遺跡に別の時代や場所の遺物を埋めて、\n自分で掘り出して「発見」したの",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "私は妻だけど、それ以前に考古学者。\n歴史を歪ませるような行為を見過ごせなかった",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "不正を認めて発見を取り下げるように\n勧めたってこと？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ええ。でも、あの人は拒否したの。\nだから……私は学会に、告発した",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "それで、あの人は学会を追われて……\n元々仲が悪かったけど、もう修復不可能になったわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "そして職を失った父さんは、\n母さんを恨むようになった……そういうこと？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そう。ひどい大ゲンカの末に、家からも出てったわ。\nだけど最近、果たし状が送られてきて――",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "念のため、代理としてカロリンさんを雇ったの。\n決闘なんて馬鹿げた話、付き合う気もないけど",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "まったくだよ……。てか、よくカロリンを雇ったね。\n確かに強いけど、シスターなのに",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "彼女とは少し縁があったから……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "！？　何ごと……！？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "……来たか。母さんはここに居て！\n私はカロリンを手伝ってくる！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "お止まりください！\nそれ以上近づくことは許しません！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの父",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "誰だお前は！　そこをどけ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "父さん、やめてよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの父",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ハ、ハイディ！？\n帰って来てくれたのか！？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "父さん……\nまさか、ゴーレムまで操るようになったの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの父",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "母さんは我が考古学を否定した！　\nゆえに我が叡智を見せてやっているのだ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "ゴーレムの使役には豊富な考古学の知識が必要です。\n自らの能力を誇示したいのですね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "だからって家の前で暴れる馬鹿がどこにいるっての！　\nカロリン、一緒に止めて！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "はい、これは説法が必要のようですね……！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]